OL,3,C'Sorry for the pain and suffering':
OL,4,CMan charged with step-daughter's murder
OL,6,FThe stepfather of Ellie Flanagan who
OL,7,Fwas murdered in Enniskillen has said
OL,8,Fhe is "sorry for all the pain and
OL,9,Fsuffering caused," a court has been
OL,10,Ftold.
OL,12,FThe 23-year-old was found dead at a
OL,13,Fhouse in Co Fermanagh town on Saturday.
OL,15,FMartin McCarney, 45, whose address
OL,16,Fcannot be made public, appeared in
OL,17,Fcourt in Strabane via video link from
OL,18,Fthe PSNI's Musgrave custody suite in
OL,19,FBelfast charged with her murder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
