OL,3,C'Sorry for the pain and suffering':
OL,4,CMan charged with step-daughter's murder
OL,6,FHe is also accused of possessing an
OL,7,Foffensive weapon - three knives with
OL,8,Fintent to commit an indictable
OL,9,Foffence, namely murder.
OL,11,FMr McCarney, wearing a grey track
OL,12,Fsuit, replied "I do" when asked if he
OL,13,Funderstood the charges against him.
OL,15,FThe defendant's solicitor told the
OL,16,Fcourt that he wanted to publicly say
OL,17,Fhe was "truly and genuinely sorry for
OL,18,Fall the pain and suffering caused to
OL,19,Fthe immediate family and community of
OL,20,FEnniskillen as a result of events of
OL,21,Fthe past week".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
