OL,3,C'Sorry for the pain and suffering':
OL,4,CMan charged with step-daughter's murder
OL,6,FThe court was told the defendant was
OL,7,Faware of the ongoing preparations on
OL,8,FThursday and Friday for the funeral.
OL,10,FPolice responded to a report of a
OL,11,Fcollision near the village of Tempo on
OL,12,FSaturday night but the driver had fled
OL,13,Fthe scene.
OL,15,FOfficers traced the vehicle that was
OL,16,Fregistered to a house in Enniskillen
OL,17,Feight miles away. Inside, they
OL,18,Fdiscovered the childcare worker's body.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/4
