OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773360185
OL,3,C'Sorry for the pain and suffering':
OL,4,CMan charged with step-daughter's murder
OL,6,FA detective constable told the court
OL,7,Fshe could connect the accused to the
OL,8,Fcharges.
OL,10,FNo application for bail was made.
OL,12,FMr McCarney was remanded in custody to
OL,13,Fappear again in Enniskillen via video
OL,14,Flink on March 30.
